<div class="alert alert-info m-alert m-alert--icon m-alert--air m-alert--square m--margin-bottom-30" role="alert">
    <div class="m-alert__icon">
        <i class="la la-warning"></i>
    </div>
    <div class="m-alert__text">
        Morris is customizable and super easy plugin to build good looking charts.
        For more info please check out <a class="m-link m-link--primary m--font-bolder" href="http://morrisjs.github.io/morris.js/" target="_blank">the official documentation.</a> 
    </div>  
    <div class="m-alert__close">
        <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="alert" aria-label="Close">
        </button>   
    </div>              
</div>

<div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-12">
